targets.query:
from(bucket: "duck_bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "temp" and
    r._field == "temp"
    )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 2m, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "duck_bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "cpu" and
    r._field == "usage_system"
    )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 2m, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "duck_bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "disk" and
    r._field == "used_percent" and
    (r.label == "rootfs" or r.label == "bootfs")
    )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 2m, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "duck_bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "swap" and
    r._field == "used_percent" and
    r.host == "duck-orchestrator"
    )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 2m, fn: mean)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _field: "swap" }))

from(bucket: "duck_bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "mem" and
    r._field == "used_percent" and
    r.host == "duck-orchestrator"
    )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 2m, fn: mean)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _field: "mem" }))

from(bucket: "duck_bucket")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "system" and
    r._field == "uptime"
    )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 2m, fn: mean)
